    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Actually, I had thought we had implemented `cythonize --with-shared` (or similar) by now, but it seems that that's still missing and `cython` is the only command that can generate the shared utility module file. Only the `cythonize()` function has it. It should be added to the `cythonize` command as well, there's no reason it should be missing there.\r\n\r\n_Originally posted by @scoder in https://github.com/cython/cython/pull/7479#discussion_r2831951597_\r\n            ",
